    "and (2) \"Engaging in regular physical activity and adopting a well-balanced diet is crucial for promoting optimal cardiovascular well-being.\"",
    "Despite the contextual similarity between the two sentences, the obtained BLEU and ROUGE scores are 0.39 and 0.13, respectively, on a scale of 0 to 1, reflecting low alignment.",
    "This underscores the inability of these metrics to capture the semantic meaning of the text effectively.",
    "Therefore, if we solely use these metrics to evaluate a healthcare chatbot, an inaccurate answer may receive a high score compared with the reference answer.",
